{"tid":1066262,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"紅線過唔到海 可以經東涌線/搭W1/坐船","createTime":"2019-03-17T21:36:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-18T00:37:33.000Z","uid":31388,"like":20,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"660af63408c0e479677710346e4eea2f342df8e9","tid":1066262,"uid":31388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T21:36:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://mobile.nwstbus.com.hk/nwp3/?f=1&amp;ds=W1&amp;dsmode=1&amp;l=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmobile.nwstbus.com.hk%2Fnwp3%2F%3Ff%3D1%26ds%3DW1%26dsmode%3D1%26l%3D0&d=0ENX7tHwQhT09cvOu3%2F4Mw5Iyec62GFiithg4eFnous%3D&h=cc233dd5\" target=\"_blank\">https://mobile.nwstbus.com.hk/nwp3/?f=1&amp;ds=W1&amp;dsmode=1&amp;l=0</a><br />\n由於中環站附近發生列車事故，荃灣綫列車服務受阻<br />\n<br />\n此訊息發放時間 : 2019-03-18 04:00<br />\n<br />\n荃灣綫服務更改如下<br />\n中環站 往返 尖沙咀站：暫停服務，請考慮使用其他交通工具<br />\n尖沙咀站 往返 荃灣站：每3.5分鐘一班，請考慮使用其他交通工具或利用港鐵網絡的其他綫路。<br />\n<br />\n發生咁大單嘢，聽朝交通肯定瀨屎瀨尿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果你而家睇到呢個post嘅，恭喜你！不如早啲出門口，及早計劃行程<br />\n<br />\n西鐵線沿線過海去港島區，有幾個方法<br />\n第一個方法，用南昌站經東涌線過海<br />\n第二個方法，可以去柯士甸站搭巴士W1<br />\n第三個方法，尖沙咀/尖東站落車，尖沙咀碼頭搭船過海，已去到中環或灣仔<br />\n<br />\n城巴W1 高鐵西九龍站&gt;皇后像廣場&gt;金鐘<br />\n<br />\n巴士路線資料：<a href=\"https://mobile.nwstbus.com.hk/nwp3/?f=1&amp;ds=W1&amp;dsmode=1&amp;l=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmobile.nwstbus.com.hk%2Fnwp3%2F%3Ff%3D1%26ds%3DW1%26dsmode%3D1%26l%3D0&d=0ENX7tHwQhT09cvOu3%2F4Mw5Iyec62GFiithg4eFnous%3D&h=cc233dd5\" target=\"_blank\">https://mobile.nwstbus.com.hk/nwp3/?f=1&amp;ds=W1&amp;dsmode=1&amp;l=0</a><br />\n<br />\n班次<br />\n7:30-11:10 每20分鐘一班<br />\n11:10-18:40 每15分鐘一班<br />\n<br />\n渡海小輪班次資料<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.starferry.com.hk/tc/service\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.starferry.com.hk%2Ftc%2Fservice&d=0ENX7tHwQhT09cvOu3%2F4Mw5Iyec62GFiithg4eFnous%3D&h=e99571b4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.starferry.com.hk/tc/service</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gbZ4V70.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgbZ4V70.png&h=9af474a0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n今次大件事，希望咁多位連登仔女守望相助！睇下可唔可以透過呢一個post發放即時交通資訊，比大家一個預算啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n另外歡迎各位補充或者提供更好方案<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e389ba87348e53342413227694aa2969d57edea5","tid":1066262,"uid":31388,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T21:43:11.000Z","msg":"觀塘線荃灣線過海去港島區，你有幾個辦法<br />\n第一個方法，最簡單可以經油塘站北角站過海去港島線<br />\n<br />\n第二個方法，荃灣線荃灣至深水埗沿途各站，可以經荔景站去東涌線過海<br />\n<br />\n第三個方法，可以搭到去黃埔站，行路去紅磡碼頭坐船由紅磡去北角，喺北角碼頭上岸後繼續坐地鐵完成行程<br />\n<br />\n關於紅磡坐船去港島區<br />\n船資料：<a href=\"http://www.starferry.com.hk/tc/service\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.starferry.com.hk%2Ftc%2Fservice&d=0ENX7tHwQhT09cvOu3%2F4Mw5Iyec62GFiithg4eFnous%3D&h=e99571b4\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.starferry.com.hk/tc/service</a><br />\n航行時間：8分鐘<br />\n<br />\n班次資料：<br />\n紅磡-&gt;北角 07:05 07:35 08:05 08:20 08:35 09:05 09:35 10:05 10:35 11:05 11:35 12:05"},{"pid":"7c0e766a1f798fcb7c1100685b6bcaacd0dc63e6","tid":1066262,"uid":31388,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T21:47:02.000Z","msg":"推上去希望船公司巴士公司運輸署會見到，加密班次或者派高運戴量巴士行走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d32091245d7dbc793599eeec13085f025cb06d08","tid":1066262,"uid":7355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e389ba87348e53342413227694aa2969d57edea5","tid":1066262,"uid":31388,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T21:43:11.000Z","msg":"觀塘線荃灣線過海去港島區，你有幾個辦法<br />\n第一個方法，最簡單可以經油塘站北角站過海去港島線<br />\n<br />\n第二個方法，荃灣線荃灣至深水埗沿途各站，可以經荔景站去東涌線過海<br />\n<br />\n第三個方法，可以搭到去黃埔站，行路去紅磡碼頭坐船由紅磡去北角，喺北角碼頭上岸後繼續坐地鐵完成行程<br />\n<br />\n關於紅磡坐船去港島區<br />\n船資料：<a href=\"http://www.starferry.com.hk/tc/service\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.starferry.com.hk%2Ftc%2Fservice&d=0ENX7tHwQhT09cvOu3%2F4Mw5Iyec62GFiithg4eFnous%3D&h=e99571b4\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.starferry.com.hk/tc/service</a><br />\n航行時間：8分鐘<br />\n<br />\n班次資料：<br />\n紅磡-&gt;北角 07:05 07:35 08:05 08:20 08:35 09:05 09:35 10:05 10:35 11:05 11:35 12:05"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T21:47:46.000Z","msg":"應該新渡輪？"},{"pid":"611f76395355214b5ab9046c62e26c3ba57e105b","tid":1066262,"uid":23271,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T21:50:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ro0LFEz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fro0LFEz.png&h=f8ebc59e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n金鐘往返尖沙咀開返喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78d2de584d998715399dc93531ff5aebdd62c401","tid":1066262,"uid":31388,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e389ba87348e53342413227694aa2969d57edea5","tid":1066262,"uid":31388,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T21:43:11.000Z","msg":"觀塘線荃灣線過海去港島區，你有幾個辦法<br />\n第一個方法，最簡單可以經油塘站北角站過海去港島線<br />\n<br />\n第二個方法，荃灣線荃灣至深水埗沿途各站，可以經荔景站去東涌線過海<br />\n<br />\n第三個方法，可以搭到去黃埔站，行路去紅磡碼頭坐船由紅磡去北角，喺北角碼頭上岸後繼續坐地鐵完成行程<br />\n<br />\n關於紅磡坐船去港島區<br />\n船資料：<a href=\"http://www.starferry.com.hk/tc/service\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.starferry.com.hk%2Ftc%2Fservice&d=0ENX7tHwQhT09cvOu3%2F4Mw5Iyec62GFiithg4eFnous%3D&h=e99571b4\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.starferry.com.hk/tc/service</a><br />\n航行時間：8分鐘<br />\n<br />\n班次資料：<br />\n紅磡-&gt;北角 07:05 07:35 08:05 08:20 08:35 09:05 09:35 10:05 10:35 11:05 11:35 12:05"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T21:51:05.000Z","msg":"唔好意思，手快打錯咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n關於紅磡坐船去港島區<br />\n船資料：<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.nwff.com.hk/route/get_route.php?id=1c87d6ed-4ace-464c-b24e-4db2b83ce902&amp;route_id=5&amp;submenu_num=3&amp;lang=zh-hke\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.nwff.com.hk%2Froute%2Fget_route.php%3Fid%3D1c87d6ed-4ace-464c-b24e-4db2b83ce902%26route_id%3D5%26submenu_num%3D3%26lang%3Dzh-hke&d=0ENX7tHwQhT09cvOu3%2F4Mw5Iyec62GFiithg4eFnous%3D&h=eef13c67\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.nwff.com.hk/route/get_route.php?id=1c87d6ed-4ace-464c-b24e-4db2b83ce902&amp;route_id=5&amp;submenu_num=3&amp;lang=zh-hke</a>"},{"pid":"ae76008d79582af9b23cb4fbde5eb87374ef043e","tid":1066262,"uid":31388,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"611f76395355214b5ab9046c62e26c3ba57e105b","tid":1066262,"uid":23271,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T21:50:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ro0LFEz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fro0LFEz.png&h=f8ebc59e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n金鐘往返尖沙咀開返喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T21:53:32.000Z","msg":"開返但係博唔過<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因為按照幾次嘅經驗都係佢寫就寫呢個班次，但係實際上嘅時間唔止<br />\n同埋要考慮埋乘客流量會倒灌，到時未入站已經大排長龍，月台都未必落到去<br />\n與其係咁，不如分散投資用其他方法過海<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你好我好大家好"},{"pid":"1ad1f32b7057b00bda09562035ff6c0a6b4ce00f","tid":1066262,"uid":31388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d32091245d7dbc793599eeec13085f025cb06d08","tid":1066262,"uid":7355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e389ba87348e53342413227694aa2969d57edea5","tid":1066262,"uid":31388,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T21:43:11.000Z","msg":"觀塘線荃灣線過海去港島區，你有幾個辦法<br />\n第一個方法，最簡單可以經油塘站北角站過海去港島線<br />\n<br />\n第二個方法，荃灣線荃灣至深水埗沿途各站，可以經荔景站去東涌線過海<br />\n<br />\n第三個方法，可以搭到去黃埔站，行路去紅磡碼頭坐船由紅磡去北角，喺北角碼頭上岸後繼續坐地鐵完成行程<br />\n<br />\n關於紅磡坐船去港島區<br />\n船資料：<a href=\"http://www.starferry.com.hk/tc/service\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.starferry.com.hk%2Ftc%2Fservice&d=0ENX7tHwQhT09cvOu3%2F4Mw5Iyec62GFiithg4eFnous%3D&h=e99571b4\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.starferry.com.hk/tc/service</a><br />\n航行時間：8分鐘<br />\n<br />\n班次資料：<br />\n紅磡-&gt;北角 07:05 07:35 08:05 08:20 08:35 09:05 09:35 10:05 10:35 11:05 11:35 12:05"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T21:47:46.000Z","msg":"應該新渡輪？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T21:56:25.000Z","msg":"冇錯係新渡輪，手快打錯，感謝巴打指正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70d6d18b5ec51e1db0edc7eb69ee21e5d7b7e091","tid":1066262,"uid":167186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T21:57:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"894b293080c7bac9b5a91414a4af7d56e182c128","tid":1066262,"uid":31388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T22:12:57.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"69f8057478a9166ddf5d12b5a7ad4d4e6d660d77","tid":1066262,"uid":54354,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T22:15:37.000Z","msg":"睇黎都係早d出門去尖咀坐船過海安全d"},{"pid":"01fa204a1cd1a012efc956e0742cf5a72d0a5a0d","tid":1066262,"uid":113040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T22:20:34.000Z","msg":"啱啱撘紅線，葵興至荔景站都喺月臺等一大輪先開車。即刻轉東涌線～<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf37aaa1697896f6b351d924566af2b263781bdb","tid":1066262,"uid":31388,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T22:30:53.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>西隧過海</strong></span><br />\n除咗上面講嘅W1 係利用西隧過海 來往 柯士甸站 中環 金鐘，仲有下列嘅巴士會途經西隧去港島區<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>上車站：西區海底隧道收費廣場（往香港島方向）</strong><br />\n最近鐵路站（依照距離排列）：九龍站，柯士甸站<br />\n<br />\n路線資料：<a href=\"https://hkbus.fandom.com/wiki/%E8%A5%BF%E5%8D%80%E6%B5%B7%E5%BA%95%E9%9A%A7%E9%81%93%E6%94%B6%E8%B2%BB%E5%BB%A3%E5%A0%B4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhkbus.fandom.com%2Fwiki%2F%25E8%25A5%25BF%25E5%258D%2580%25E6%25B5%25B7%25E5%25BA%2595%25E9%259A%25A7%25E9%2581%2593%25E6%2594%25B6%25E8%25B2%25BB%25E5%25BB%25A3%25E5%25A0%25B4&d=0ENX7tHwQhT09cvOu3%2F4Mw5Iyec62GFiithg4eFnous%3D&h=b2b7711a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hkbus.fandom.com/wiki/%E8%A5%BF%E5%8D%80%E6%B5%B7%E5%BA%95%E9%9A%A7%E9%81%93%E6%94%B6%E8%B2%BB%E5%BB%A3%E5%A0%B4</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>九巴由西九龍新區、荃灣、葵青往灣仔路線</strong><br />\n914、914P、914X、934、934A、935、936、936A、948、948A、948B、948P、948X<br />\n<br />\n<strong>九巴由屯門、元朗、新界東往灣仔／東區路線</strong><br />\n307C、960、960C、960P、960S、960X、961、961P、968、968A、968X、978、978A、978B、980A、980X、981P、982X、985<br />\n<br />\n<strong>城巴往金鐘／灣仔路線</strong><br />\n930、930A、930X、962A、967、969A、969B<br />\n<br />\n<strong>城巴獨營，往銅鑼灣／東區路線</strong><br />\n962、962B、962E、962P、962S、962X、967X、969、969P、969X、A11、A12、E11、E11A、E11S<br />\n<br />\n<strong>九龍往西區及灣仔路線</strong><br />\n904、905、905P <br />\n<br />\n<strong>新巴城巴往南區路線</strong><br />\n970、970X、971、A10、973<br />\n<br />\n你亦都可以利用九巴，新巴城巴app 去搵啱用路線同到站時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83062c666eec5858a7a834fd7d40d571a49803c9","tid":1066262,"uid":31388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"01fa204a1cd1a012efc956e0742cf5a72d0a5a0d","tid":1066262,"uid":113040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T22:20:34.000Z","msg":"啱啱撘紅線，葵興至荔景站都喺月臺等一大輪先開車。即刻轉東涌線～<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T22:32:54.000Z","msg":"巴打醒目<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fdc1342832049317d6f38d2de2d2fcc009c47bca","tid":1066262,"uid":31388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T22:36:10.000Z","msg":"推上去希望船公司巴士